               <p>I am a <rs id="t17860222-47-viclabel263" type="occupation">publican</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-47-victim596 t17860222-47-viclabel263"></join>, I keep the <placeName id="t17860222-47-crimeloc264">Green Dragon, on St. Andrew's-hill, Black-friars</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17860222-47-crimeloc264" type="placeName" value="Green Dragon, on St. Andrew's-hill, Black-friars"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17860222-47-crimeloc264" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-47-off261 t17860222-47-crimeloc264"></join>; I saw the prisoner in my house on Tuesday last, the 21st instant, about three; I was shewn some pots by Mr. White, which were mine, I have seen the prisoner at my house before; he says, he is a bricklayer, I am sure when I went out, the day I lost the pots, I left him in the house.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860222-47-person598">
                  JOHN
                   WHITE
